<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>و ز ر<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[٥٥٩٢ - و ز ر]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>وزَرَ يَزِر، زِر، وَزْرًا ووِزْرًا، فهو وازِر، والمفعول مَوزور <span class="c2">(للمتعدِّي)</span><a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">• وزَر الشَّخصُ:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>١ - حمل ما يُثْقل ظهره من الأشياء المُثْقِلة.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>⦗٢٤٣٠⦘ ٢ - أَثِم.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">• وزَر الشَّيءَ:</span> حَمَلهُ <span class="c1">" <span class="c3">{وَلاَ تَزِرُ وَازِرَةٌ وِزْرَ أُخْرَى}</span>: لا تُؤاخذ نفسٌ بذنب أخرى"</span>.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c5">• وزَر الرَّجُلَ:</span> غَلَبه.<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>